lead_paragraph: McConnell, a rookie filling in for the injured Ish Smith, scored 17 points for Philadelphia, which earned an eighth win while ending a four-game losing streak.

headline.print_headline: Rookie Inspires 76ers to Hold On and Defeat Nets
